On behalf of Renewal SA, CBRE are pleased to present you with a ground floor tenancy of 441sqm in the Administration Building in Australia's leading and most awarded innovation district at Tonsley.

Available immediately, the tenancy is afforded with a practical and flexible layout that consists of open plan and partitioned office space, complimented with meeting rooms and utility space.

Excellent natural light penetrates the tenancy with the entrance located immediately to the right of the building’s main entrance. On-site parking is available for occupiers.

The Tonsley precinct brings together leading-edge research and education institutions, established businesses and start-ups, business incubators and accelerators, as well as government and the wider community to connect, collaborate and innovate. Tonsley Innovation District's masterplan incorporates collaborative meeting and working spaces providing world-class facilities to help take great new ideas from concept and testing to market.

This is an opportunity for companies that exist in Tonsley’s four focus sectors of health, medical devices and assistive technology, cleantech and renewable energy, automation, software and simulation, mining and energy services to join the likes of SAGE, Siemens, ZEISS, SIMEC ZEN Energy, Tesla, Micro-X, as well as Flinders University and TAFE SA. 

Please refer to the Tonsley website to determine if your organisation meets the district's suitability criteria - tonsley.com.au
